frames.caption: A massive stone structure resembling a temple is being lifted by a giant stone figure emerging from the ground. Debris and dust fill the air as the structure ascends, with glowing inscriptions visible on the figure's body.

frames.description: The scene depicts a gigantic stone statue rising from the ocean, lifting a temple structure above its head. The glowing inscriptions on the statue add a magical element, while the surrounding ocean and distant structures create an epic and grand atmosphere.
